title: >>> Your OFFICIAL Poster
body_text:
Congratulations to Justin Pierce, who got the most number of votes in the "DODGEBALL 17 Poster" Contest! His "Fear the Bullet" poster took home the gold and is now the official DODGEBALL 17 Poster.
Kathleen Reinhard came in a nice second place finish with her design (#7).
Ryan Letsche was only one vote short of Kathleen as his design (#6) landed him third.
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
3rd PLACE:
2nd PLACE:
WINNER:
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
The Full Results:
#3 ... 38% (Design by Justin Pierce)
#7 ... 19% (Design by Kathleen Reinhard)
#6 ... 17% (Design by Ryan Letsche)
#4 ... 9% (Design by Kathleen Reinhard)
#1 ... 9% (Design by Diana DiBuccio)
#2 ... 5% (Design by Kathleen Reinhard)
#8 ... 3% (Design by Diana DiBuccio)
#5 ... 0% (Design by Diana DiBuccio)
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
The poster has been decided ... all that is left is the event itself ...
Who's ready for 17 ?
